author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! I've been saying since I first saw the initial announcement that Rockstar would delay this behemoth of a game. Thankfully we still have a release date that came out of this somehow even though we all would love to see some more screenshots. I'm still excited and hopefully this delay leads to a better game. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: GTA 6 Got Delayed...
